            . I am a servant to 
               <persName id="t18150405-116-person1041">
                  Thomas 
                  Neale
               <interp inst="t18150405-116-person1041" type="surname" value="Neale"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-116-person1041" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-116-person1041" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , I have the care of his pigs, on the night before this happened, I saw them all safe in the stye at six o'clock; on the morning of the 26th, I found I had lost four pigs, when I got them again, three were alive, and one dead.</p>

